        "body": "<p>Instead of using only <code>DESC<\/code>, you will have to describe according to which attribute you want to sort data. So instead use this:<\/p>\n<pre><code>Cursor cursor = contentResolver.query(uri, null, null, null, MediaStore.Video.Media.DATE_ADDED + &quot; DESC&quot;);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
